Description: 
  With blank todos items, the deleting mark "X" does not align with the row of the item.
  
Step to reproduce:
1. Browse to http://todomvc.com/examples/angular2/
      
2. Add some items.
      
3. Make an item blank by double clicks the item and remove the string.
  
4. Move the mouse cursor over the blank item to display the deleting mark "X".
   Expected Result: "X" should be aligned with the row of the blank item.
   
In the step 4. The "X" does not align.
